# Database

- `packages/database` contains Supabase/PostgreSQL migrations and is not a pnpm workspace package.
- Make schema changes as new SQL migrations under `packages/database/supabase/migrations/`; do not edit historical migrations unless explicitly asked.
- Keep row level security explicit for user-owned data.
- When adding tables that reference users, model ownership deliberately and include policies in the same migration.
- Treat recordings, transcripts and structured AI outputs as sensitive data.
- Coordinate app code changes with migration changes so column names, status values and access policies stay aligned.
